fn000117 1 N000055 105.351 106.658 <o,compq,native_children,M> elf biggenu
fn000117 1 N000055 107.564 109.455 <o,compq,native_children,M> begin beginnen
fn000117 1 N000055 109.837 111.851 <o,compq,native_children,M> dat is mooi zeug.
fn000117 1 N000055 113.509 113.878 <o,compq,native_children,M> tien
fn000117 1 N000055 114.562 117.114 <o,compq,native_children,M> vette en één dunne bigu
fn000117 1 N000055 117.517 118.005 <o,compq,native_children,M> big.
