fn000117 1 N000055 259.434 260.181 <o,compq,native_children,M> Bolla
fn000117 1 N000055 260.584 262.159 <o,compq,native_children,M> Bol-lands
fn000117 1 N000055 262.159 263.170 <o,compq,native_children,M> dik zijn.
fn000117 1 N000055 263.591 265.476 <o,compq,native_children,M> en de mensen ook.
