fn100227 1 N100052 457.512 458.968 <o,compq,native_elderly,F> in juni negentien nee
fn100227 1 N100052 458.968 461.326 <o,compq,native_elderly,F> vier en negen-tigs
fn100227 1 N100052 461.326 463.446 <o,compq,native_elderly,F> uit de notering te halen.
