fn100234 1 N100054 483.903 485.712 <o,compq,native_elderly,M> na die grote lekkage
fn100234 1 N100054 485.712 487.270 <o,compq,native_elderly,M> was het dure behang
fn100234 1 N100054 487.270 488.690 <o,compq,native_elderly,M> aan vervanging toe.
